# ğŸ¤– AI Automated Code Repair Agent

![AI Code Repair Agent Banner](https://placehold.co/1200x300/0f172a/ffffff?text=AI+Automated+Code+Repair+Agent&font=raleway)

**AI Automated Code Repair Agent** is a professional, autonomous CLI tool that executes Python scripts, detects crashes, and uses an AI-driven workflow to analyze, repair, and **securely verify fixes** before recommending them. It packages everything you needâ€”from intelligent error parsing to isolated Docker-based verificationâ€”so you can point it at a script and get reliable, reproducible results.

**PyPI Package:** [**ai-code-repair-agent**](https://pypi.org/project/ai-code-repair-agent/)

---

## âœ¨ Core Features

- **ğŸ¤– Autonomous End-to-End Workflow:** Run `agent <script.py>` and let the tool handle execution, crash detection, analysis, patching, and reporting.
- **ğŸ§  AI-Powered Code Generation (Gemini):** Sends rich error context to Google's **Gemini LLM** to propose logical, high-quality fixesâ€”not just syntax band-aids.
- **ğŸ›¡ï¸ Secure Sandbox Verification:** Builds an **isolated Docker container** on the fly, runs tests, and **accepts only verified solutions**.
- **ğŸ”® Auto-Dependency & Environment Discovery:** Inspects the target script to infer thirdâ€‘party dependencies and autoâ€‘generate `requirements.txt` and a `Dockerfile`.
- **ğŸ¯ Environment-Aware Diagnostics:** Distinguishes code bugs from environment issues (e.g., **ModuleNotFoundError**) and recommends precise `pip install` commands when appropriate.
- **ğŸ“¦ Professional CLI Experience:** Distributed via PyPI with a user-friendly `agent configure` command for easy setup and a built-in Docker prerequisite check.

