## ğŸ” Example Module Layout

```
ai_code_repair_agent/
â””â”€ agent/
   â”œâ”€ __init__.py
   â”œâ”€ cli.py              # CLI orchestrator, configure command, Docker check
   â”œâ”€ process_runner.py   # Run target script, capture outputs
   â”œâ”€ error_parser.py     # Parse tracebacks
   â”œâ”€ context_manager.py  # Extract faulty function via AST
   â”œâ”€ ai_core.py          # Prompt & call Gemini, load API key
   â”œâ”€ sandbox_verifier.py # Build Docker envs & verify
   â””â”€ reporter.py         # Colorized results & diffs
```

---

## ğŸ§± Security & Privacy

- **No source exfiltration:** Only error-specific context is sent to the AI.
- **Ephemeral sandboxes:** Containers are temporary and removed post-execution.
- **Secrets management:** API keys securely stored in a `.env` file in your home directory.

